filament_end_gcode:
; Filament-specific end gcode 
;END gcode for filament
filament_start_gcode:
; Filament gcode
;M412 D10  ;10mm distance
;M412 S1   ; Enable runout
;M900 K0.10 ; Linear advance spring constant - tested

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_MK2.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0645{endif}  ; set cybermk2 advance
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_E3DD.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.07{endif}  ; set E3DD advance
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_MK2.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.6} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.042{endif}  ;guess
name: 3D Tomorrow Silk
